title: mbp 2011 17" not turning on
message: Probably not using an ORIGINAL Apple 85W charger, must use 85W or it will not turn on if battery is empty.

title: mbp 2011 17" not turning on
message: First check what date code is on the GPU. If this is still a 2011 one then you can put time and effort into this thing and it will have a dead GPU in 3 months.
